---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro'
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Adaptive Alchemy LLC collects, uses, and protects information on this website."
>
  <section class="px-6 py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-text-primary md:text-5xl">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-text-muted">Last updated: April 17, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-10 text-text-muted">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-serif text-xl text-text-primary">Who we are</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            This website is operated by Adaptive Alchemy LLC, a Wyoming limited
            liability company. Our business address is 30 N Gould St #24790,
            Sheridan, WY 82801. You can reach us at{' '}
            <a href="tel:+13074540093" class="text-gold hover:underline">
              (307) 454-0093
            </a>{' '}
            or{' '}
            <a
              href="mailto:inquiries@adaptivealchemy.io"
              class="text-gold hover:underline"
            >
              inquiries@adaptivealchemy.io
            </a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-serif text-xl text-text-primary">
            What we collect and why
          </h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            We collect only information you actively provide. When you contact
            us by email, we receive your name, email address, and the contents
            of your message. We use this information solely to respond to your
            inquiry and, if a business relationship follows, to conduct that
            work.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            We do not use analytics software, advertising trackers, or any
            third-party scripts that collect behavioral data about visitors to
            this site. We do not set cookies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-serif text-xl text-text-primary">
            Hosting and server logs
          </h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            This site is hosted on GitHub Pages. GitHub may collect standard
            server log data (IP address, browser type, referring URL, and
            timestamp) as part of normal hosting operations. This data is
            governed by{' '}
            <a
              href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement"
              class="text-gold hover:underline"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              GitHub&rsquo;s Privacy Statement
            </a>. We do not access or process these server logs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-serif text-xl text-text-primary">
            How we store and protect your data
          </h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Email correspondence is stored in our business email system. We
            retain it for as long as it is relevant to an active or potential
            business relationship, and delete it when it is no longer needed. We
            do not sell, rent, or share your information with third parties for
            marketing purposes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-serif text-xl text-text-primary">Your rights</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            If you are in the European Economic Area or United Kingdom, you have
            rights under GDPR to access, correct, or delete personal data we
            hold about you, and to object to or restrict its processing. To
            exercise any of these rights, email us at{' '}
            <a
              href="mailto:inquiries@adaptivealchemy.io"
              class="text-gold hover:underline"
            >
              inquiries@adaptivealchemy.io
            </a>. We will respond within 30 days.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-serif text-xl text-text-primary">Changes</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            If we materially change this policy, we will update the date at the
            top of this page. Continued use of the site after a change
            constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
